<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-03-0497 </DOCNO><TEXT>Presents disaster and production statistics for Japan. Discusses the researchand development programmes of the Coal Mining Research Centre, Japanwithin safety and production technology, including prevention of gasand rock outbursts; spontaneous combustion and mine fire prevention;roadway maintenance technology for deep coal mines and temperature loweringcountermeasures; application of safety equipment to coal mines; laboursaving and automation; labour reduction; automation and remote-controltechniques of drifting and transport; coal mining techniques for steepseams; coal mining techniques for gently dipping seams. Also reportson research and development in coal mines; research and development programmesof manufacturers; and related areas of research and development.</TEXT></DOC>